    "citation" : "Sven E. Avak, Jurg C. Trachsel, Jacinta Edebeli, Sabina Brutsch, Thorsten Bartels-Rausch, Martin Schneebeli, Margit Schwikowski, Anja Eichler. 2019. Melt-Induced Fractionation of Major Ions and Trace Elements in an Alpine Snowpack. Journal of Geophysical Research: Earth Surface. . doi: 10.1029/2019JF005026",
    "type" : "publication",
